items.sentence: I'm not sure that anyone would want to do that.
The keys aren't on the table where I left them.
I'm going to town for flour and other supplies.
I'm so drunk that I can't feel my face anymore.
I'm fighting mad because someone stole my bike.
I'm worried about the safety of the passengers.
I'm not here to help you. I'm here to stop you.
I'm certain that your intentions are honorable.
I'm still having the same dream about drowning.
I'm going to teach you how to fish next Sunday.
